Drain BUSH'S(R) Best Blackeye Peas. Add chopped celery and onion. Combine oil, vinegar, mayonnaise, salt and cayenne. Mix well. Pour over peas. Stir gently. Allow to chill in refrigerator several hours or overnight. At serving time, add the diced tomato. Mix carefully. Serve as a relish with meats, or garnish with lettuce and a spoonful of mayonnaise and serve as a salad.